metadata.name: Apes Wildin'
metadata.description:
Apes Wildin’ is a full-send adrenaline mission into the chaotic unknown. Fuck a flow state, this song is a call of action to tap into all that is being alive. Drop in and rip that shit like it’s nobody's business!

Let this Music NFT be a tribute to moments of send, letting go of all that clouds to charge with confidence into the unknown… 

Created by @shark

@shark or @sharkofthebay is a digital artist, musician, web3 advocate, and extreme sports patron.
